txt.en: The spider-haunts of Lhingris present the adventurers of Middle-earth with both great challenges and great rewards.
You have done much to aid the Conquest of Gorgoroth in Lhingris.
You have slain many foes in the jagged heights and shadowed depths of Lhingris.
You have explored all of Lhingris.
The spider-haunts of Lhingris present the adventurers of Middle-earth with both great challenges and great rewards.
